WEBVTT

00:01.542 --> 00:03.208
(narrator)
Previously on "Hellcats  ...  "

00:03.208 --> 00:04.250
They're sisters?

00:04.250 --> 00:06.667
You're not the only one
with a complicated family.

00:06.667 --> 00:08.834
I took a bunch
of pregnancy tests

00:08.834 --> 00:10.500
and they all said positive.

00:10.500 --> 00:12.834
- Wanna tell me who the guy was?
- That doesn't matter.

00:12.834 --> 00:15.542
- How's Travis working out?
- Best server I got.

00:15.542 --> 00:17.667
- Good roommate too.
- I'm sorry.

00:17.667 --> 00:19.834
You know, I'm sure all brides
get nervous on the day.

00:19.834 --> 00:23.041
Well, I just thought that
I had more time to be sure.

00:23.041 --> 00:27.375
- Is it Red Raymond?
- I'm sorry.

00:27.375 --> 00:30.542
- That's Noah.
- As in ex-boyfriend Noah?

00:30.542 --> 00:32.165
What about the connection
we have?

00:32.165 --> 00:33.458
We've always had.
I wanna grow old with you.

00:33.458 --> 00:35.458
I don't know
what to say to that.

00:35.458 --> 00:37.041
(Vanessa)
To beat Mem-Chris,
we have to pull off

00:37.041 --> 00:39.291
the routine of our lives.
Zero margin for error.

00:39.291 --> 00:41.291
The Lancer Hellcats win it!

00:41.291 --> 00:42.583
We're going to Nationals!

00:43.708 --> 00:45.583
