up to the chest.

00:55.041 --> 00:58.625
♪ She's hot to touch
can't get enough ♪

00:58.625 --> 01:00.166
Arms shake
and make your head drop.

01:00.166 --> 01:01.917
♪ She's radical ♪

01:01.917 --> 01:04.750
♪ She's hot to touch
